Someone reviewed this and compared it to the Carry On films. This is Carry On at its worst. The puns are lame and the double entendres are single at best. Don't waste your time, even if you are an aspiring historian early naughty sex films.

This is a pretty decent skin film.  The nudity is top notch, the film is well-written and well shot and the premise is amusing.
